  "text": "This study was undertaken to observe whether EA would affect the expression of P450arom and P450c17a and their mRNA expression in PCOS ovarian tissues using letrozole, a non-steroidal aromatase inhibitor, as a reference for preparing a PCOS animal model (similar to that of Kafali [CITATION_1] ). In this study, we accounted for the following factors: the PCOS ovarian tissue morphology and structural changes, ovarian expression of P450arom, P450c17a and their mRNA, and steroid hormones (i.e., testosterone, androstenedione, estradiol, and estrone) levels related to the synthesis or catalysis of the 2 enzymes.",
